com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.coverage
Class CoverageFeature

java.lang.Object
  com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.coverage.CoverageFeature

public class CoverageFeature
extends java.lang.Object

Contains information about a Feature which has or participates in one or more coverage gaps. (E.g. has one or more segments along its edge which form a gap or overlap with another feature).
